OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain. Dry start Tuesday but becoming
OL,8,Fwindier as rain spreads east. Windy on
OL,9,FWednesday as rain clears to sunny
OL,10,Fspells and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
